<item>
            <title>[CXF-3750] Sometimes, CXF servlet will blocked until bussiness logical finished for one-way operation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-3750</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sometime,the servlet handle(JettyHTTPHandler) at server side doesn&apos;t return back to servlet engine(Jetty) immediately, it will waiting until the asynchrouse business logical finished; &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;CXF2.3.3 windows xp, jdk1.5_22 or jdk1.6_17&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12519374">CXF-3750</key>
